{{DISPLAYTITLE:A_TeloSpawnA}}
'''A_TeloSpawnA'''
(no parameters)

Spawns a {{Class|TelOtherFX3}} at the calling actor's position. The spawned FX has its parent actor's angle and <tt>target</tt> field, and half its speed. Its <tt>special1</tt> field is set to 1; this is used as a countdown by [[A_CheckTeleRing]].

